uiries: please email the church office: <a href=\"mailto:ichurchleiden@gmail.com\">ichurchleiden@gmail.com</a>\n\nFor pastoral matters: please ring your Life Group Leader. If not applicable or you wish to make an appointment to speak with one of the pastoral team, please contact the church office via email.\n\n</div>','Contact','','inherit','open','open','','6-autosave','','','2012-07-09 20:04:36','2012-07-09 19:04:36','',6,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=39',0,'revision','',0),(75,1,'2012-08-17 19:16:24','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2012-08-17 19:16:24','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=75',0,'post','',0),(50,1,'2012-07-09 19:47:46','2012-07-09 18:47:46','Follow?\r\n\r\nIf you are a follower of football, then you will know that Spain were champions in Kiev.\r\nIf you are a follower of tennis, then Wimbledon is your thing right now!\r\nIf you are a follower of athletics, then the Olympics in London will no doubt be grabbing your attention later this month.\r\nKeeping the football theme, Ronaldo is amongst the top 20 people being followed on Twitter. Though above him are various pop stars as well as President Obama and Ophrah Winfrey!\r\n\r\nIn life more generally, who or what do you follow?\r\n\r\nIn the church world, there is often talk of being a follower of Jesus Christ.\r\nNow when it comes to sport, to describe someone as a follower could mean a casual fan or someone for whom it is a passion that shapes his or her life......\r\nHow about following Christ? Is it just another fan option like football or Formula 1?\r\nIf you or I say that we are followers of Christ, what do we mean by that? More importantly what does Christ mean when He calls us to follow?\r\n‘Come follow me’ are some of the earliest recorded words of Christ in Matthew’s Gospel.\r\nWill we follow? Do we? Dare we?\r\nWill we follow whatever the cost?\r\nWill we follow wherever that leads?\r\nPerhaps it is good in coming weeks to reflect. Why not reflect on a passage from the Bible like Matthew chapters 5 to 7? I\'d like to suggest we all do this whether we are a Christian or we are exploring whether Christianity might be real or not.\r\n\r\nWill we follow Him?\r\n\r\nAndy','Follow','','publish','open','open','','follow','','','2012-07-09 19:47:46','2012-07-09 18:47:46','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=50',0,'post','',0),(40,1,'2012-07-09 19:17:42','2012-07-09 18:17:42','<div id=\"lipsum\">\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed elementum vulputate libero in eleifend. Quisque luctus consectetur purus nec viverra. Nunc viverra mi ac mauris rutrum commodo. Suspendisse vel pharetra sem. Quisque tellus felis, semper et blandit sed, molestie vitae velit. Suspendisse porttitor, velit sit amet placerat pharetra, nulla felis dictum leo, id cursus dolor metus sit amet elit. Vestibulum molestie lorem sit amet diam dignissim sed aliquet<a title=\"Hello world!\" href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/?p=1\"> nisi molestie.</a>\r\n\r\nDonec orci orci, pulvinar ac malesuada et, semper et velit. Etiam vitae metus lacus. Phasellus ac eros urna. Fusce aliquam semper arcu, nec mollis dolor tempor vel. Suspendisse hendrerit feugiat orci vel ultricies. Vivamus nulla nisi, volutpat sit amet dapibus sed, accumsan aliquam elit. Sed sit amet lorem id erat rutrum accumsan a et nulla. Curabitur condimentum nibh in dolor ultricies eget feugiat tellus tristique. Ut id sagittis diam. Vestibulum tincidunt aliquet porttitor. Vivamus euismod interdum sem et aliquet. Nulla et est magna, id porttitor dolor.\r\n\r\nEtiam sed malesuada sem. Quisque sed neque arcu. Morbi sed quam lorem. Praesent malesuada vehicula nunc, sed bibendum lacus lobortis nec. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Curabitur eu diam eu nibh congue ultricies. Quisque faucibus pharetra dictum. Praesent feugiat elementum laoreet. Mauris vitae lacus eget libero dapibus facilisis. Maecenas vel quam erat. Vivamus et consequat purus