40 and Ephesians 4:1-16 (why not look these up!)\n\nCore values/culture:\n\nUnderpinning our culture as a community are the following core values:\n<blockquote>REAL - seeking to be open and honest without the need to pretend or play religious games\n\nFAMILY - a relational community of all ages drawn from many nations\n\nSIMPLE - a style of church that is uncomplicated and relevant for 21st Century life\n\nPASSION - hearts stirred to see others impacted by Christ</blockquote>\nA bit more on who we are....\n\nICL began in 2004 in the home of Tim and Marketa Southerland who were here serving as missionaries from the USA (Assemblies of God World Missions). Tim sensed as the first pastor that a key Bible phrase for the church was \"a planting of the Lord for the display of His splendour\" (Isaiah 61:3b). We continue to walk with this as a foundational Scripture for ICL\'s existence.\n\nAs an international church, the make up of our community has many different nationalities. We use English as a common language though all of our kids ministry and youth is bi-lingual with Dutch as the other language.\n\nWe are part of the local church in the Leiden area and desire to serve alongside others to see this area impacted by Jesus Christ. Partnering includes through the Leaders Prayer Network, Serve the City and HiP.\n\nA heart for mission means a concern for our community but also for elsewhere in the Netherlands and in other countries, such as partnering with Convoy of Hope as well as other missionaries and projects we support.\n\nWe are a member of the <a href=\"http://www.vpe.nl\">VPE</a>, a network of Pentecostal/Evangelical churches in the Netherlands. We are also a partner church in the Fellowship of European International Churches(<a href=\"http://www.feic.org\">www.feic.org</a>) To see our statement of faith, which is in keeping with that of the VPE, click on <a href=\"http://www.ichurchleiden.nl/webelieve.html\">We believe</a>.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2012-07-09 21:31:19','2012-07-09 20:31:19','',2,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=71',0,'revision','',0),(72,1,'2012-07-09 20:52:35','2012-07-09 19:52:35','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-8','','','2012-07-09 20:52:35','2012-07-09 19:52:35','',2,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=72',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2012-07-09 20:24:10','2012-07-09 19:24:10','<div id=\"lipsum\">\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed elementum vulputate libero in eleifend. Quisque luctus consectetur purus nec viverra. Nunc viverra mi ac mauris rutrum commodo. Suspendisse vel pharetra sem. Quisque tellus felis, semper et blandit sed, molestie vitae velit. Suspendisse porttitor, velit sit amet placerat pharetra, nulla felis dictum leo, id cursus dolor metus sit amet elit. Vestibulum molestie lorem sit amet diam dignissim sed aliquet nisi molestie.\r\n\r\nDonec orci orci, pulvinar ac malesuada et, semper et velit. Etiam vitae metus lacus. Phasellus ac eros urna. Fusce aliquam semper ar